	I '''Emile Berliner''' ([[Mayu 20]], [[1851]] – [[Agostu 3]], [[1929]]) metung yang  [[Germany|aleman]]-bait [[United States|American]]ung  [[manimbentu]], mas kebaluan keng kayang pamanalkus keng [[gramophone record|disc record]] [[gramophone]] (''[[phonograph]]'' keng [[American English]]). Iya ing mitatag keng [[Berliner Gramophone]] Company inyang 1895, Ing [[Gramophone Company]] king [[London, England]], inyang 1897, [[Deutsche Grammophon]] king [[Hanover]], [[Germany]], inyang 1898 ampong [[Berliner Gramophone#Berliner Gram-o-phone Company of Canada|Berliner Gram-o-phone Company ning Canada]] king [[Montreal, Quebec|Montreal]] inyang 1899.


[[Image:Schellackplatte 1908.jpg|thumb|Ing plaka megawa inyang 1908 king Hanover, Germany neng Emile Berliner's Gramophone Company (kaibat [[Deutsche Grammophon]])]]

